    "description": "Welcome to join our official discord server to find friends to play together:<br><br>Get ready for the exciting world of Combo Bombo! Engage in thrilling multiplayer battles with friends, using creative and powerful weapon combinations to dominate the competition.<br><br><strong>Combine Items into Powerful Weapons</strong><br>With our innovative weapon combining system, you can mix and match items to create powerful tools of destruction. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/44e682afc961026422c26265688c34b7.poster.avif?t=1683418906\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/44e682afc961026422c26265688c34b7.webm?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/44e682afc961026422c26265688c34b7.mp4?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Online multiplayer battle</strong><br>Join the fun and battle it with your friends in our online multiplayer mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/53958dd9e1d54160e9f12de752d60424.poster.avif?t=1683418906\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/53958dd9e1d54160e9f12de752d60424.webm?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/53958dd9e1d54160e9f12de752d60424.mp4?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Different mini-games</strong><br>And don't forget about our exciting mini-games! Complete them to earn points and gain an edge over your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/28e20cde9e0d32791950d72d67220537.poster.avif?t=1683418906\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/28e20cde9e0d32791950d72d67220537.webm?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/28e20cde9e0d32791950d72d67220537.mp4?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With two levels, five mini-games, and ten unique weapons waiting for you, Combo Bombo offers endless hours of thrilling gameplay. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/c52ca402cb965384e9482820cbcc95d4.poster.avif?t=1683418906\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/c52ca402cb965384e9482820cbcc95d4.webm?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/c52ca402cb965384e9482820cbcc95d4.mp4?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Don't miss out on the fun!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/ad93ffecb27e170d8d4a852b787c3c4d.poster.avif?t=1683418906\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/ad93ffecb27e170d8d4a852b787c3c4d.webm?t=1683418906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359300/extras/ad93ffe